                .withExposedPorts(PORT)
                .withCommand(USER + &quot;:&quot; + PASSWORD + &quot;:1001:::upload&quot;);



When you need an FTPS server or any other protocoll, you can pick another image like this for example and adapt the container configuration. [https://hub.docker.com/r/bozorgiyan/ftps-server][2]


